  "original_title": "Three arrested in relation to Ambalangoda shooting incident",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three arrested in relation to Ambalangoda shooting incident",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): Three suspects have been arrested in connection with a shooting incident in Urawatte, Ambalangoda, where one person died.",
        "Police said that the three suspects, aged between 21 and 41 years, were arrested while lodging at a house in Gemunu Mawatha, Homagama.",
        "The police also stated that a 64-year-old female residing in the house, where the suspects were hiding, was arrested on the charges of sheltering and aiding them.",
        "Moreover Police have seized a pistol manufactured overseas, a bag of ammunition, the motorcycle used for the crime, and three mobile phones which were used to commit the crime.",
        "The police said that the suspects are scheduled to be produced before the Magistrate's Court today (20)."
      ],
